.TH "LIGHTNING-PAYMENT-RETRY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-payment-retry \- retry a payment by re-sending the BOLT 11 invoice
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning payment-retry
.I bolt11
.SH DESCRIPTION
Re-attempts payment of a BOLT 11 invoice via
.BR pay .
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-pay (1),
.BR lightning-payment-list-failed (1)
